  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK328">
<l>naṉṟāku mākkam periteṉiṉuñ cāṉṟōrkkuk</l>
<l>koṉṟāku mākkaṅ kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The advantage which might flow from destroying life in sacrifice, is dishonourable to the wise (who renounced the world), even although it should be said to be productive of great good.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
